tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE Order_Item (
  order_item_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  order_id INT,
  product_id INT,
  quantity INT,
  price DECIMAL
);
